children.chars:
A single SKU with flexible term durations for all of Trend Vision One consolidates the purchasing process.
Simplified licensing entitlements leverage a single license activation process. Say goodbye to individual license keys.
Implementation flexibility allows you to adjust credit allocations on-demand. No more fixed license counts. No more underutilized licenses. Easier, broader adoption.
XDR standalone purchase options lower the barrier of entry for security organizations interested in Trend Vision One without a ‘rip and replace’ proposition, particularly for endpoint protection.  Contact our sales team for more information. To learn more about credit-based licensing, see the online help.

children.name: What are credits? Credits are the universal licensing unit used to purchase XDR sensors and supported features.
children.chars:
What are credits?
Credits are the universal licensing unit used to purchase XDR sensors and supported features.

children.name: How do credits impact my existing licenses? Credits offer the exact same benefits as a standard XDR subscription but with added flexibility.
children.chars: How do credits impact my existing licenses? Credits offer the exact same benefits as a standard XDR subscription but with added flexibility.

children.name: How can I use credits to deploy features in Trend Micro Vision One? Enable the XDR sensors and supported features that you require directly from your console. Credits are applied automatically and a live summary can be viewed at any time in the Credit Usage app.
